data.revised_prompt: An eye-catching, professional-grade culinary photograph. At the center of the composition is a bowl of hearty Orange Chicken and Rice Soup. The chicken should look tender, succulent, and imbued with orange tanginess. The rice, scattered throughout the soup, adds texture, and the appetizing, steaming broth ties it all together. The supporting elements around the bowl include fresh greens, thoughtful cutlery, and an elegant cloth napkin, creating a well-executed snapshot of an inviting meal.
